1:Last week, some of our cameras with default or simple password have been attacked, caused those cameras offline or password been changed problem.
2:We have updated the APP, add the Password check function, the default or simple password camera will be forbided to use, also improved the server's security level .
3:If your camera with offline problem or simple password recently, suggest that reset your camera and change the password immediately.
